  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t社会坠入疯癫“革命”前后，女性从优雅变身丑陋, 人间地狱之别：<br/>\r\n第一张照片下方英文：Delight(?) of Cuba’s loveliest society girls gather in a Havana garden to compare notes on their new clothes, most of which come direct from Paris.<br/>\r\n古巴最可爱的社交妇女们欢聚哈瓦那一花园中，品评各自多直源于巴黎的新装。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n第二张照片网上说明：1950s Photography，Vintage Cuba / models of the store ''Fin de Siglo'' (Havana. CA. 1956)<br/>\r\n1950年代古巴珍品照/时尚百货商场 “Fin de Siglo“ 的模特们（哈瓦那，1956年前后）。<br/>\r\n（<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly90cmFuc2xhdGluZ2N1YmEuY29tL29uY2UtdGhlLWpld2VsLW9mLWN1YmFuLWRlcGFydG1lbnQtc3RvcmVzLWZpbi1kZS1zaWdsby1oYXMtYmVjb21lLWEtZHVtcC8\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://translatingcuba.com/once-the-jewel-of-cuban-department-stores-fin-de-siglo-has-become-a-dump/\">参看始建于1897年的西班牙语世界第一时尚百货商场Fin de Siglo【意为“世纪之交”】辉煌的历史与残败的今天</a>)<br/>\n<br/>\r\n正所谓：<br/>\n<b>燕瘦环肥清凉会</b><br/>\n<b>风姿仪态笑盈园</b><br/>\n<b>时尚裙沿花争艳</b><br/>\n<b>自由世上自然开</b>。<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9WcjU1aGRkLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vr55hdd.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vr55hdd.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vr55hdd.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9nNlh0Q2VjLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/g6XtCec.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/g6XtCec.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/g6XtCec.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n这风姿仪采，尽毁于癫狂血腥共产革命，叹。<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS95SllFb041LmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/yJYEoN5.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/yJYEoN5.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yJYEoN5.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9Cdk9RcUZELmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/BvOQqFD.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/BvOQqFD.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BvOQqFD.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS81M2MzQnhFLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/53c3BxE.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/53c3BxE.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/53c3BxE.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a>&lt;—这一边一块疙瘩肉咧笑的荷枪女下方西班牙语似乎写的是“古巴妇女联盟”？<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS85ZUx6UnVTLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/9eLzRuS.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/9eLzRuS.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9eLzRuS.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n时光未必总向前<br/>\r\n泼皮革命经常赢<br/>\r\n当年文明潮多远<br/>\r\n恶棍祸世退百年<br/>\n<br/>\r\n参见：<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/63171\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/63171\"><b>风华绝代上海滩</b></a> </div>",
